        <!-- Q7 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    <m> \displaystyle\int_{0}^{2} x \sqrt{2 x-x^{2}} \mathrm{~d} x=\frac{\pi}{2} </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解
                <me> 
                \begin{aligned}
                \int_{0}^{2} x \sqrt{2 x-x^{2}} \mathrm{~d} x  &amp;  =\int_{0}^{2} x \sqrt{1-(x-1)^{2}} \mathrm{~d} x \xlongequal{t=x-1} \int_{-1}^{1}(t+1) \sqrt{1-t^{2}} \mathrm{~d} t \\
                &amp;  =0+\int_{-1}^{1} \sqrt{1-t^{2}} \mathrm{~d} t=\frac{\pi}{2} .
                \end{aligned}
                </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q8 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    计算  <m> \displaystyle\int_{0}^{1} \sqrt{x} \mathrm{e}^{\sqrt{x}} \mathrm{~d} x </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    &amp;  \int_{0}^{1} \sqrt{x} \mathrm{e}^{\sqrt{x}} \mathrm{~d} x \xlongequal[x=u^{2}]{u=\sqrt x } \int_{0}^{1} u \mathrm{e}^{u} 2 u \mathrm{~d} u=2 \int_{0}^{1} u^{2} \mathrm{e}^{u} \mathrm{~d} u \\
                    =  &amp;  2\left[\left.u^{2} \mathrm{e}^{u}\right|_{0} ^{1}-2 \int_{0}^{1} u \mathrm{e}^{u} \mathrm{~d} u\right]=2\left[\mathrm{e}-0-2\left(\left.u \mathrm{e}^{u}\right|_{0} ^{1}-\int_{0}^{1} e^{u} \mathrm{~d} u\right)\right] \\
                    =  &amp;  2\left[\mathrm{e}-2\left(\mathrm{e}-\left.\mathrm{e}^{u}\right|_{0} ^{1}\right)\right]=2[\mathrm{e}-2 \mathrm{e}+2(\mathrm{e}-1)]=2(\mathrm{e}-2)
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q9 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    计算  <m> \displaystyle\int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \sqrt{x^{2}+1} d x </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    <me> 
                        \begin{aligned}
                        \because \int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \sqrt{x^{2}+1} \mathrm{~d} x &amp; =\left.x \sqrt{x^{2}+1}\right|_{0} ^{\frac{4}{3}}-\int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} x \mathrm{~d}\left(\sqrt{x^{2}+1}\right) \\
                         &amp; =\frac{4}{3} \cdot \frac{5}{3}-\int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \frac{x^{2}}{\sqrt{x^{2}+1}} \mathrm{~d} x=\frac{20}{9}-\int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \frac{x^{2}+1-1}{\sqrt{x^{2}+1}} \mathrm{~d} x \\
                         &amp; =\frac{20}{9}-\int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \sqrt{x^{2}+1} \mathrm{~d} x+\int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \frac{1}{\sqrt{x^{2}+1}} \mathrm{~d} x \\
                        \therefore \int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \sqrt{x^{2}+1} \mathrm{~d} x &amp; =\frac{10}{9}+\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{\frac{4}{3}} \frac{1}{\sqrt{x^{2}+1}} \mathrm{~d} x=\frac{10}{9}+\left.\frac{1}{2} \ln \left(x+\sqrt{x^{2}+1}\right)\right|_{0} ^{\frac{4}{3}} \\
                        \end{aligned}
                         </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q10 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设  <m> f(x) </m>  连续,  <m> g(x)=\int_{0}^{1} f(x t) \mathrm{d} t </m> , 且  <m> \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{f(x)}{x}=A </m> . (  <m>  A  </m>  为常数), 求  <m> g^{\prime}(x) </m>  并讨论  <m> g^{\prime}(x) </m>  在  <m> x=0 </m>  处的连续性. 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: 由  <m> \lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{f(x)}{x}=A </m>  , 知 <m> f(0)=0 </m> ,  <m> g(0)=\int_{0}^{1} f(0) \mathrm{d} t=0 </m>  .
                    令   <m> u=x t </m>  , 得  <m> g(x)=\frac{\int_{0}^{x} f(u) \mathrm{d} u}{x}(x \neq 0) </m>  . 
                    于是  <m> x \neq 0 </m>   时,   <m> g^{\prime}(x)=\frac{x f(x)-\int_{0}^{x} f(u) \mathrm{d} u}{x^{2}} </m> , 当  <m> x=0 </m>   时, 
                    <me>  g^{\prime}(0)=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{g(x)-g(0)}{x-0}=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\int_{0}^{x} f(u) \mathrm{d} u}{x^{2}}=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{f(x)}{2 x}=\frac{A}{2} </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q11 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设  <m> f(x) </m>  在  <m> (-\infty,+\infty) </m>  内连续, 且  <m> F(x)=\int_{0}^{x}(x-2 t) f(t) \mathrm{d} t </m> , 
                    证明: (1) 若  <m> f(x) </m>  为偶函数, 则  <m> F(x) </m>  也是偶函数; </p> 
                    <p> (2) 若  <m> f(x) </m>  非增, 则  <m> F(x) </m>  非减. 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证:(1)
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    F(-x) &amp; =  \int_{0}^{-x}(-x-2 t) f(t) \mathrm{d} t \\
                    &amp;  \xlongequal{\text { 令 } u=-t}-\int_{0}^{x}(-x+2 u) f(-u) \mathrm{d} u \\
                    &amp;  \xlongequal{f(-u)=f(u)} \int_{0}^{x}(x-2 u) f(u) \mathrm{d} u=F(x),
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 所以  <m> F(x) </m>  是偶函数. </p> 

                    <p> (2) 
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    \because F^{\prime}(x) &amp; =\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d} x}\left[x \int_{0}^{x} f(t) \mathrm{d} t-2 \int_{0}^{x} t f(t) \mathrm{d} t\right] \\
                    &amp; =\int_{0}^{x} f(t) \mathrm{d} t+x f(x)-2 x f(x)=\int_{0}^{x} f(t) \mathrm{d} t-x f(x) \\
                    &amp; \xlongequal{\text { 积分中值定理 }} f(\xi) x-x f(x)=x[f(\xi)-f(x)],
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 其中  <m> 0 \leq \xi \leq x </m> , 或  <m> x \leq \xi \leq 0 </m> . 又因为  <m> f(x) </m>  非增, 于是  <m> \forall x \in \mathbf{R} </m> , 当  <m> x \leq 0 </m>  时,  <m> f(\xi) \leq f(x) </m> ,此时,  <m> F^{\prime}(x)=x[f(\xi)-f(x)] \geq 0 </m> ; 而当  <m> x \geq 0 </m>  时,  <m> f(\xi) \geq f(x) </m> ,这时也有  <m> F^{\prime}(x)=x[f(\xi)-f(x)] \geq 0 </m> ; 所以,  <m> F(x) </m>  非减. 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q12 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    已知  <m> f(x)=\displaystyle\int_{1}^{x} \sqrt{1+t^{4}} d t </m> , 则  <m> \displaystyle\int_{0}^{1} x^{2} f(x) d x= </m>
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解:  <m> f(1)=0 ,f^{\prime}(x)=\sqrt{1+x^{4}} </m>  </p> 

                <p>  <me> 
                \begin{aligned}
                \int_{0}^{1} x^{2} f(x) d x &amp; =\int_{0}^{1} f(x) d \frac{x^{3}}{3}=\left.f(x) \frac{x^{3}}{3}\right|_{0} ^{1}-\int_{0}^{1} \frac{x^{3}}{3} d f(x)\\
                &amp; =0-\int_{0}^{1} \frac{x^{3}}{3} f^{\prime}(x) d x\\
                &amp; =-\int_{0}^{1} \frac{x^{3}}{3} \sqrt{1+x^{4}} d x=-\frac{1}{12} \int_{0}^{1} \sqrt{1+x^{4}} d\left(1+x^{4}\right) \\
                &amp; =-\left.\frac{1}{12} \frac{2}{3}\left(1+x^{4}\right)^{\frac{3}{2}}\right|_{0} ^{1}=\frac{1-2 \sqrt{2}}{18} .
                \end{aligned}
                </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q13 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    求   <m> I=\displaystyle\int_{-\frac{\pi}{4}}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{-x}} d x </m> 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解:

                <me> I=\int_{-\frac{\pi}{4}}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{-x}} d x=\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{-x}} d x+\int_{-\frac{\pi}{4}}^{0} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{-x}} d x  </me>  </p> 

                <p>  <me> \int_{-\frac{\pi}{4}}^{0} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{-x}} d x \xlongequal{\text { 令 } t=-x}-\int_{\frac{\pi}{4}}^{0} \frac{\sin ^{2} t}{1+e^{t}} d t=\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} t}{1+e^{t}} d t=\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{x}} d x  </me>  </p> 

                <p>  <me>  \begin{aligned}\text { 原式 } I &amp; =\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{-x}} d x+\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{1+e^{x}} d x\\ &amp; =\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \sin ^{2} x\left(\frac{1}{1+e^{-x}}+\frac{1}{1+e^{x}}\right) d x\\ &amp; =\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}} \sin ^{2} x d x \\  &amp; =\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{4}}(1-\cos 2 x) d x\\ &amp; =\left.\left(\frac{x}{2}-\frac{1}{4} \sin 2 x\right)\right|_{0} ^{\frac{\pi}{4}}=\frac{\pi}{8}-\frac{1}{4} .\end{aligned}  </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q14 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设  <m> f(x) </m>  为区间  <m> [-1,1] </m>  上取正值的连续函数, 求  <m> I=\displaystyle\int_{-1}^{1} \frac{f(x) \cos x+\sin ^{7} x}{f(x)+f(-x)} d x </m> 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解:  <m> \frac{\sin ^{7} x}{f(x)+f(-x)} </m>  奇函数, 在  <m> [-1,1] </m>  上积分为零 </p> 

                    <p>  <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    I &amp; =\int_{-1}^{1} \frac{f(x) \cos x}{f(x)+f(-x)} d x \xlongequal{\text { 令 } t=-x}-\int_{-1}^{-1} \frac{f(-t) \cos (-t)}{f(-t)+f(t)} d t =\int_{-1}^{1} \frac{f(-t) \cos (t)}{f(-t)+f(t)} d t \\
                    2 I &amp; =\int_{-1}^{1} \frac{f(x) \cos x}{f(x)+f(-x)} d x+\int_{-1}^{1} \frac{f(-x) \cos x}{f(-x)+f(x)} d x =\int_{-1}^{1} \cos x d x=2 \sin 1 .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q15 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设  <m> y^{\prime}(x)=\arctan (x-1)^{2} </m> , 且  <m> y(0)=0 </m> , 求  <m> \displaystyle\int_{0}^{1} y(x) d x </m> . 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: 
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    &amp;  \left.\int_{0}^{1} y(x) d x \xlongequal{\text { 直接分部积分 }} x y(x)\right|_{0} ^{1}-\int_{0}^{1} x y^{\prime}(x) d x=y(1)-\int_{0}^{1} x \arctan (x-1)^{2} d x \\
                    &amp;  =y(1)-\int_{0}^{1} x \arctan (x-1)^{2} d x \\
                    &amp;  =y(1)-\int_{0}^{1}(x-1) \arctan (x-1)^{2} d x-\int_{0}^{1} \arctan (x-1)^{2} d x \quad \boxed{\int_{0}^{1} y^{\prime}(x) d x=y(1)-y(0)} \\
                    &amp;  =-\int_{0}^{1}(x-1) \arctan (x-1)^{2} d x \xlongequal{t=x-1}-\int_{-1}^{0} t \arctan t^{2} d t \\
                    &amp;  =-\frac{1}{2} \int_{-1}^{0} \arctan t^{2} d t^{2}=\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{1} \arctan v d v \\
                    &amp;  =\left.\frac{1}{2} v \cdot \arctan v\right|_{0} ^{1}-\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{1} \frac{v}{1+v^{2}} d v\\ &amp; =\frac{\pi}{8}-\left.\frac{1}{4} \ln \left(1+v^{2}\right)\right|_{0} ^{1}=\frac{\pi}{8}-\frac{1}{4} \ln 2
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q16 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    计算由曲线  <m> y=4-x^{2} </m>  与  <m> y=3 x </m>  所围图形的面积  <m> S </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 解方程组  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{l}y=4-x^{2} \\ y=3 x\end{array}\right. </m> , 得二曲线的交点  <m> (-4,-12),(1,3) </m> . </p> 

                    <p>  <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    S  &amp;  =\int_{-4}^{1}\left[\left(4-x^{2}\right)-3 x\right] \mathrm{d} x \\
                    &amp;  =\int_{-4}^{1}\left(4-3 x-x^{2}\right) \mathrm{d} x \\
                    &amp;  =4(1-(-4))-\left.\frac{3}{2} x^{2}\right|_{-4} ^{1}-\left.\frac{1}{3} x^{3}\right|_{-4} ^{1} \\
                    &amp;  =20-\frac{3}{2}(1-16)-\frac{1}{3}(1+64)=\frac{125}{6} .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q17 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    求摆线的一拱 <m> \left\{\begin{array}{l}x=a(t-\sin t), \\y=a(1-\cos t)\end{array}(0 \leq t \leq 2 \pi)\right. </m>  与  <m> O x </m>  轴所围图形的面积  <m> A </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    A  &amp;  =\int_{0}^{2 \pi} a(1-\cos t)[a(t-\sin t)]^{\prime} \mathrm{d} t=a^{2} \int_{0}^{2 \pi}(1-\cos t)^{2} \mathrm{~d} t \\
                    &amp;  =a^{2} \int_{0}^{2 \pi}\left(1-2 \cos t+\cos ^{2} t\right) \mathrm{d} t \\
                    &amp;  =a^{2}\left[2 \pi-0+\int_{0}^{2 \pi} \frac{1+\cos 2 t}{2} \mathrm{~d} t\right] \\
                    &amp;  =3 \pi a^{2} .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q18 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    求由心形线  <m> \rho=a(1+\cos \theta) </m>  所围图形的面积  <m> S </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 :
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    S  &amp;  =\frac{1}{2} \int_{0}^{2 \pi} \rho^{2}(\theta) \mathrm{d} \theta \\
                    &amp;  =\frac{1}{2} a^{2} \int_{0}^{2 \pi}(1+\cos \theta)^{2} \mathrm{~d} \theta \\
                    &amp;  =\frac{1}{2} a^{2} \int_{0}^{2 \pi}\left(1+2 \cos \theta+\cos ^{2} \theta\right) \mathrm{d} \theta \\
                    &amp;  =\frac{1}{2} a^{2}[2 \pi+0+\pi] \\
                    &amp;  =\frac{3}{2} \pi a^{2}
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q19 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    求由椭圆  <m> \frac{x^{2}}{a^{2}}+\frac{y^{2}}{b^{2}}=1 </m>  所围图形分别绕  <m> O x </m>  和  <m> Oy </m>  轴旋转而成旋转体  <m> \Omega_{1} </m>  和  <m> \Omega_{2} </m>  (旋转椭球体) 的体积  <m> V_{x} </m>  和  <m> V_{y} </m> . 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
