                &amp; =\left.\ln |\sec x+\tan x|\right|_{0} ^{\frac{\pi}{6}}=\ln \left|\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\right|\\ &amp; =\ln \sqrt{3}=\frac{1}{2} \ln 3 . 
                \end{aligned} </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

