        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    一个横放的圆柱形水桶内盛有半桶水. 设桶的底半径为  <m> R </m> , 水的比重为  <m> \gamma </m> , 求桶的一个端面上所受的压力  <m> F </m> . 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解：被水挤压的半圆的方程为
                <me> 
                y=\sqrt{R^{2}-x^{2}}(0 \leq x \leq R) .
                </me>  </p> 

                <p> 由对称性, 有
                <me> 
                \begin{aligned}
                F  &amp;  =2 \int_{0}^{R} \gamma x \sqrt{R^{2}-x^{2}} \mathrm{~d} x \\
                &amp;  =-\gamma \int_{0}^{R} \sqrt{R^{2}-x^{2}} \mathrm{~d}\left(R^{2}-x^{2}\right)=-\left.\frac{2 \gamma}{3}\left(R^{2}-x^{2}\right)^{\frac{3}{2}}\right|_{0} ^{R} \\
                &amp;  =\frac{2}{3} \gamma R^{3} .
                \end{aligned}
                </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>


